{{Lunar May}} '''Lunar May''' (旧暦五月) is the fifth {{ill|Month (Calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月}} of the year in the {{ill|Japanese Calendar|ja|和暦}} (the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|太陰太陽暦}}’s {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}}).
The month that includes the {{ill|Summer Solstice|ja|夏至}} becomes May. In the {{ill|Gregorian Calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} ({{ill|New Calendar|ja|新暦}}), it corresponds approximately to late {{ill|May|ja|5月}} to early {{ill|July|ja|7月}}.
