{{Lunar May}} '''Lunar May''' (旧暦五月) is the fifth {{ill|Month (Calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月}} of the year in the {{ill|Japanese Calendar|ja|和暦}} (the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|太陰太陽暦}}’s {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}}).
The month that includes the {{ill|Summer Solstice|ja|夏至}} becomes May. In the {{ill|Gregorian Calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} ({{ill|New Calendar|ja|新暦}}), it corresponds approximately to late {{ill|May|ja|5月}} to early {{ill|July|ja|7月}}.
Another name for May is {{nihongo|'''Satsuki'''|さつき}}. The origin of the name is explained in {{ill|May|ja|5月}}.
In the {{ill|Eastern|ja|東洋}} {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|太陰太陽暦}}, because the number of days in a month, known as {{ill|Large and Small|ja|大小}} (with large months having 30 days and small months 29 days), varies each year, there are years in which May ends on the 29th and May 30th does not exist. [[ja:5月 (旧暦)]] == Satsuki Dates == {| class="wikitable" |+ Satsuki Dates ! Gregorian Year !! New Moon !! Last Day !! Number of Days |- | 2014 || {{ill|May 29|ja|5月29日}} || {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日}} || 29 days |- | 2015 || {{ill|June 16|ja|6月16日}} || {{ill|July 15|ja|7月15日}} || 30 days |- | 2016 || {{ill|June 5|ja|6月5日}} || {{ill|July 3|ja|7月3日}} || 29 days |- | 2017 || {{ill|May 26|ja|5月26日}} || {{ill|June 23|ja|6月23日}} || 29 days |- | 2017 ([[Leap month|leap]]) || {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日}} || {{ill|July 22|ja|7月22日}} || 29 days |- | 2018 || {{ill|June 14|ja|6月14日}} || {{ill|July 12|ja|7月12日}} || 29 days |- | 2019 || {{ill|June 3|ja|6月3日}} || {{ill|July 2|ja|7月2日}} || 30 days |- | 2020 || {{ill|June 21|ja|6月21日}} || {{ill|July 20|ja|7月20日}} || 30 days |- | 2021 || {{ill|June 10|ja|6月10日}} || {{ill|July 9|ja|7月9日}} || 30 days |- | 2022 || {{ill|May 30|ja|5月30日}} || {{ill|June 28|ja|6月28日}} || 30 days |- | 2023 || {{ill|June 18|ja|6月18日}} || {{ill|July 17|ja|7月17日}} || 30 days |- | 2024 || {{ill|June 6|ja|6月6日}} || {{ill|July 5|ja|7月5日}} || 30 days |- | 2025 || {{ill|May 27|ja|5月27日}} || {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日}} || 29 days |} [[cdo:Nùng-lĭk 5 nguŏk hak]] [[gan:五月]] [[hak:Nùng-la̍k 5-ngie̍tja]] [[ja:5月 (旧暦)]] [[ko:음력 5월]] [[th:เดือน 5]] [[vi:Tháng năm]] [[wuu:农历五月]] [[za:Ndwenngu]] [[zh-min-nan:Kū-le̍k 5 goe̍h]] [[zh-yue:五月]] [[zh:农历五月]]
